<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Page de Validation d'Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: large;
            font-family: 'Arial', 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            margin: 0;
        }

        video {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .formulaire {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            box-shadow: 0px 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .formulaire h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .formulaire span {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #ff5722;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        input[type="email"] {
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #fff;
            background-color: transparent;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        input[type="email"]:focus {
            border-color: #ff5722;
            outline: none;
        }

        button {
            padding: 15px 25px;
            background-color: #ff5722;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #b43109;
            color: white;
        }

        #message {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            color: rgb(222, 67, 67);
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .formulaire {
                width: 90%;
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }

            .formulaire h2 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            input[type="email"] {
                font-size: 1rem;
                padding: 12px;
            }

            button {
                font-size: 1rem;
                padding: 12px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<video autoplay loop muted>
    <source src="/font/6917189_Motion Graphics_Motion Graphic_3840x2160.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    Votre navigateur ne prend pas en charge la vidéo.
</video>

<div class="formulaire">
    <h2>Vérifiez votre adresse email</h2>
    <form id="formulaire" action="setPassWord" method="post">
        <span>Veuillez entrer l'adresse email que vous avez utilisée lors de votre enregistrement.</span>
        <input type="email" name="email" id="email" placeholder="Adresse Email" required>
        <button type="submit">Valider</button>
        <span id="message">{{message}}</span>
    </form>
</div>

</body>
</html>
